<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <body>
        <div id="main">
            <h1 id="header">Verify Your Email</h1>
            <p>Hello,</p>
            <p>Welcome to ChatBox! Keep your account secure by activating your email with the link below</p>
            </br>
            <div id="verifyContainer">
                <a id="verify" href="%%REPLACEME%%">Verify Email</a>
            </div>
            <p id="expDisclaimer">This link will expire in 30 minutes</p>
            </br>
            <p>Link not working? Paste this URL into your browser: %%REPLACEME%%</p>
            <p>Still need help? You can email support at %%SUPPORTEMAIL%%</p>
            <p>If you did not sign up for ChatBox using your email or received this email by mistake, you do not have to do anything else. You can safely delete this email</p>
            </br>
            <p>Sincerely,</p>
            <p>The ChatBox Team</p>
        </div>
    </body>
    <style>
        p, h1, a {
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
        }
        body {
            background: #ccc;
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        #main {
            background: #eee;
            width: 90%;
            margin: 2.5%;
            padding: 2.5%;
            height: 100%;
        }

        #header {
            margin: 0;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 3em;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.25em;
        }

        #verifyContainer {
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        #verify {
            background: #287eed;
            color: white;
            font-size: 2em;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: .5em 1em;
            border-radius: 1vw;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            transition: .2s;
        }

        #verify:hover {
            filter: brightness(1.15)
        }

        #expDisclaimer {
            opacity: 0.5;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</html>